abstract: Despite being the biggest star on Current TV, Keith Olbermann is not scheduled to anchor the channel’s coverage of the Iowa caucus or the New Hampshire primary in January.
snippet: Despite being the biggest star on Current TV, Keith Olbermann is not scheduled to anchor the channel’s coverage of the Iowa caucus or the New Hampshire primary in January.
lead_paragraph: 6:05 p.m. | Updated  Keith Olbermann, who came to Current TV this year to remake the channel and compete against his old home, MSNBC, is sitting out the biggest political nights of the season.

headline.main: An Election Year Dawns Without Keith Olbermann
